1. To add the Identity providers, go to idp folder and configure identity provider configuration in identity-provider.xml
   and run the IDPAutomate.sh file.
2. To add the Service providers go to sp folder and configure service provider configuration in service-provider.xml
   and run the IDPAutomate.sh file.

All the necessary paths will read from setup.conf file that resides in deployment directory.
You can customize the public certificate path, key store file path, host name, admin user, password etc.. from that file(setup.conf)